Package: endogenr
Title: A Dynamic Endogenous Simulator of Statistical Models
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Jonas", "Vestby", , "jonves@prio.org", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-3054-977X"))
Description: This package allows you to dynamically simulate a set of statistical or mathematical models. The simulator schedules the simulation based on a network graph, and uses the R formula language as the main tool for defining models.
